[Information contained in a previous post from the Japanese Ministry of Health, Labour and Welfare noted the person with symptoms of pneumonia this individual had close contact with was his father. It is unclear if his father is part of the group of now 45 (see below) confirmed cases of novel CoV infection in Wuhan City, Hubei, China or if his father had contact in the Huanan Wholesale Seafood Market.

As mentioned above and in many other official and unofficial documents on this outbreak and novel coronavirus, we are very early in learning about this virus in terms of epidemiology (host and possible intermediary host), demographics of cases, clinical spectrum of disease including demographics of severe clinical presentations, and transmissibility of the virus, to mention a few. Remember, on a global level, we've only known about this outbreak for less than 3 weeks, and about the virus approximately 10 days. - Mod.MPP]

