[It is not surprising that additional cases have been identified in Wuhan where this outbreak appears to have begun, especially with the identification of cases in other countries in individuals travelling from Wuhan, China. One wonders if there are cases in other provinces of China that haven't been identified as yet. We await further information from China as to whether screening in other locations outside of Wuhan has begun. - Mod.MPP]

